incidents.name: [Global][Domains] - Domains Name incident notification on .hr domains

incident_updates.body: We have determined the origin of the incident affecting our Domains offer. Here are some supplementary details : Start time : 24/03/2025 10:00 UTC Impacted Services : .hr domains are not currently available for registration or transfer. We apologise for any inconvenience caused and appreciate your understanding.
